
Note, $MC corresponds to /home/angelos/GIT/membrane_project

1) Create a run directory <rundir>
2) cd <rundir>
3) Execute: source $MC/bin/setup.csh
4) You end up inside the a src directory. Now choose a config file
   from the $MC/config directory
5) Then run:
   ln -s $MC/config/config.angelos config.angelos
6) If you want to run:
   make -f makefile
   mv main ../
   cd ..
   ./main

